menu "Motor controller"

config MOTORCTRL_WIFI_SSID
    string "WiFi SSID"
    default ""
    help
        WPA2-Personal SSID for the wireless control link. Leave empty
        to skip WiFi bring-up; the firmware continues to work over the
        existing USB-serial path.

config MOTORCTRL_WIFI_PASSWORD
    string "WiFi password"
    default ""
    help
        WPA2-Personal passphrase. Stored in the local sdkconfig only —
        do not commit a populated sdkconfig.

endmenu
